<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ekstrakurikuler Sekolah</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #003366;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content-container {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .wrapper-ekskul {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3b5998;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .section-title i {
            color: #e91e63;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    .contenttt-line {
        width: 100px;
        height: 4px;
        background-color: #e91e63;
        margin: -10px auto 5px auto; 

}
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .section-title {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container content-container">
    <div class="wrapper-ekskul">
        <div class="section-title">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i> Ekstrakurikuler
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">

            <!-- Pramuka -->
            <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-compass"></i> Pramuka
                    </div>
                    <div class="contenttt-line"></div>
                    <p>
                        Pramuka adalah kegiatan yang mengajarkan keterampilan alam bebas, kerja sama, dan disiplin.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Badminton -->
            <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR75flQ6T-SHqno7TdBn8PqxYOSHrJi_PD_FQ&s" alt="Badminton">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-basketball-ball"></i> Badminton
                    </div>
                    <div class="contenttt-line"></div>
                    <p>
                        Badminton sebagai olahraga yang mengutamakan kecepatan, ketepatan, dan ketahanan tubuh.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Silat -->
            <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Silat">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-fist-raised"></i> Silat
                    </div>
                    <div class="contenttt-line"></div>
                    <p>
                        Silat adalah seni bela diri tradisional yang juga mengajarkan tentang kebudayaan dan ketahanan mental.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Tari -->
            <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Tari">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <i class="fas fa-theater-masks"></i> Tari
                    </div>
                    <div class="contenttt-line"></div>
                    <p>
                        Ekstrakurikuler Tari memfokuskan pada pengembangan seni gerak tubuh dalam berbagai bentuk tari tradisional.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
